{"tid":896928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實許冠傑嘅《半斤八兩》好馬克思主義feel","createTime":"2018-11-10T13:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T13:42:15.000Z","uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"157fa2a2c6e94d14c9f67cbc3d0eed4466d99427","tid":896928,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"「出左半斤力想話囉番足八兩 家陣惡搵食邊有半斤八兩咁理想」<br />\n--&gt;剝削剩餘價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我地呢班打工仔 一生一世為錢幣做奴隸」<br />\n--&gt;人嘅勞動唔再係為咗自我實現／將內心嘅理念具現化<br />\n而係為咗換取金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nproduct同勞動者之間出現異化<br />\n正如馬克思於一百七十多年前描述道：「工人越想賺錢，就需要犧牲更多的餘裕與自由，為貪欲而工作得像奴隸一樣。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n／&ldquo;The more they want to earn the more they must sacrifice their time and freedom and work like slaves in the service of avarice.&rdquo;／<br />\n（Economic and Philosophic Manuscripts of 1844，&ldquo;Wages of Labour&rdquo;）"},{"pid":"7a7e68ebb7874dbe9b023b30fac7ecd335ca2052","tid":896928,"uid":29606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdac66936653c764de36046b34b6ae5508f286dd","tid":896928,"uid":22356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"出半斤力攞八兩....無知一問，共產唔係出半斤力定一兩力都係攞八兩咩？"},{"pid":"7d69ed850dd3c7aef4ad55990f8f3da88f8e0001","tid":896928,"uid":22356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"自己眼殘，我自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585abb0254b536a8dae107ffc3a0f4fe9b16ed2d","tid":896928,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdac66936653c764de36046b34b6ae5508f286dd","tid":896928,"uid":22356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"出半斤力攞八兩....無知一問，共產唔係出半斤力定一兩力都係攞八兩咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:21:49.